make_limited_and_equip(string sFile, int iLimit)

  An lfun defined for monsters. Clones an object into the monster
  using make_limited_obj with the limit iLimit and then proceeds
  to have the monster equip the object. See make_limited_obj for 
  more details about limited objects.

  Note: Like make_limited_obj, this lfun returns 0 when it cannot
        create a new clone. Useful for cloning non-limited items
        on failure.

  Example: 
           make_limited_and_equip("/obj/sword",4);

           if(!make_limited_and_equip("/obj/platemail", 5))
             make_and_equip("/obj/leather");


See also: make_limited_obj, make_and_equip, make_unique_and_equip
